    <main class="content-wrap">
      <article class="card">
        <section class="section">
          <h2>App Store Purchases</h2>
          <p>MasterCourse subscriptions are sold through the Apple App Store. Because Apple processes the transaction directly, ONE MISSION GROUP LTD. does not have the ability to issue refunds on Apple's behalf.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2>How to Request a Refund</h2>
          <p>All refund requests must be submitted to Apple through their official support channel.</p>
          <p>Visit <a href="https://reportaproblem.apple.com/">reportaproblem.apple.com</a> and sign in with the Apple ID used for the purchase.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2>Cancellation vs. Refund</h2>
          <p>Canceling a subscription stops future renewals, but it does not automatically create a refund. If you want money returned for a past charge, you must file a refund request with Apple.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <h2>Questions</h2>
          <p>If you need general support relating to your subscription, contact <a href="mailto:mikebrown4342@gmail.com">mikebrown4342@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </section>
